            <fieldset class="fieldset" style="" id="fieldset1"><div class="field ui-field-contain" id="div1" req="1" topic="1" data-role="fieldcontain" type="1"><div class="field-label">1、	姓名、邮箱<span class="req">*</span></div><div class="ui-input-text" style="position:relative;"><input type="text" id="q1" value="" name="q1"></div><div class="errorMessage"></div></div><div class="field ui-field-contain" id="div2" req="1" topic="2" data-role="fieldcontain" type="3"><div class="field-label">2、	您是通过什么途径报名参与空中课堂？<span class="req">*</span></div><div class="ui-controlgroup"><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="1" id="q2_1" name="q2" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q2_1">A、	志愿者</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="2" id="q2_2" name="q2" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q2_2">B、	朋友推荐</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="3" id="q2_3" name="q2" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q2_3">C、	微信公众号推送</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="4" id="q2_4" name="q2" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q2_4">D、	微信群、QQ群推荐</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="5" id="q2_5" name="q2" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q2_5">E、	其他</div></div></div><div class="errorMessage"></div></div><div class="field ui-field-contain" id="div3" req="1" topic="3" data-role="fieldcontain" type="3"><div class="field-label">3、	您在学习课程时，一般通过哪种途径学习？<span class="req">*</span></div><div class="ui-controlgroup"><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="1" id="q3_1" name="q3" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q3_1">A、	空中课堂网站</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="2" id="q3_2" name="q3" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q3_2">B、	迈徳医学V微信公众号</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="3" id="q3_3" name="q3" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q3_3">C、	空中课堂云课堂微信公众号</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="4" id="q3_4" name="q3" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q3_4">D、	医学志愿者微信公众号</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="5" id="q3_5" name="q3" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q3_5">E、	每周电话外呼学习</div></div></div><div class="errorMessage"></div></div><div class="field ui-field-contain" id="div4" req="1" topic="4" data-role="fieldcontain" type="3"><div class="field-label">4、	您认为学习方式是否便捷？<span class="req">*</span></div><div class="ui-controlgroup"><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="1" id="q4_1" name="q4" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q4_1">A、	非常编辑</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="2" id="q4_2" name="q4" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q4_2">B、	一般</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="3" id="q4_3" name="q4" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q4_3">C、	便捷</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="4" id="q4_4" name="q4" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q4_4">D、	非常不便捷</div></div></div><div class="errorMessage"></div></div><div class="field ui-field-contain" id="div5" req="1" topic="5" data-role="fieldcontain" type="3"><div class="field-label">5、	对于课程设置，您觉得哪一课程获益最大？<span class="req">*</span></div><div class="ui-controlgroup"><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="1" id="q5_1" name="q5" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q5_1">A、	公开课</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="2" id="q5_2" name="q5" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q5_2">B、	答疑课</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="3" id="q5_3" name="q5" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q5_3">C、	私教课</div></div></div><div class="errorMessage"></div></div><div class="field ui-field-contain" id="div6" req="1" topic="6" data-role="fieldcontain" type="3"><div class="field-label">6、	对于空中课堂6大专题课程，您最喜欢哪个专题？<span class="req">*</span></div><div class="ui-controlgroup"><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="1" id="q6_1" name="q6" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q6_1">A、	糖尿病基础知识</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="2" id="q6_2" name="q6" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q6_2">B、	糖尿病的药物治疗</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="3" id="q6_3" name="q6" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q6_3">C、	糖尿病管理</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="4" id="q6_4" name="q6" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q6_4">D、	糖尿病并发症管理</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="5" id="q6_5" name="q6" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q6_5">E、	特殊类型／人群糖尿病</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="6" id="q6_6" name="q6" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q6_6">F、	其他内分泌疾病</div></div></div><div class="errorMessage"></div></div><div class="field ui-field-contain" id="div7" req="1" topic="7" data-role="fieldcontain" type="3"><div class="field-label">7、如果给2017空中课堂课程评分，您会如何评定？<span class="req">*</span></div><div class="ui-controlgroup"><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="1" id="q7_1" name="q7" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q7_1">A、100分</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="2" id="q7_2" name="q7" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q7_2">B、90分</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="3" id="q7_3" name="q7" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q7_3">C、80分</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="4" id="q7_4" name="q7" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q7_4">D、70分</div></div><div class="ui-radio"><span class="jqradiowrapper"><input type="radio" value="5" id="q7_5" name="q7" style="display:none;"><a class="jqradio" href="javascript:;"></a></span><div class="label" for="q7_5">E、60分以下</div></div></div><div class="errorMessage"></div></div><div class="field ui-field-contain" id="div8" req="1" topic="8" data-role="fieldcontain" type="1"><div class="field-label">8、关于空中课堂课程内容、授课形式等您有哪些建议？<span class="req">*</span></div><div class="ui-input-text" style="position:relative;"><input type="text" id="q8" value="" name="q8"></div><div class="qinsert">提示：例如：增加病种、增加病例解读等</div><div class="errorMessage"></div></div></fieldset>
